{"legislative_session": "119", "identifier": "HR 2262", "title": "Flexibility for Workers Education Act", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["bill"], "subject": [], "abstracts": [], "other_titles": [{"note": "", "title": "To amend the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 to exclude certain activities from hours worked, and for other purposes."}], "other_identifiers": [{"identifier": "ocd-bill-us-119-hr2262"}], "actions": [{"description": "Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.", "date": "2026-01-13T22:52:11+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "On passage Failed by the Yeas and Nays: 209 - 215 (Roll no. 19).", "date": "2026-01-13T22:52:09+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Failed of passage/not agreed to in House On passage Failed by the Yeas and Nays: 209 - 215 (Roll no. 19).", "date": "2026-01-13T22:52:09+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "On motion to recommit Failed by the Yeas and Nays: 209 - 213 (Roll no. 18).", "date": "2026-01-13T21:59:35+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Considered as unfinished business. (consideration: CR H692-693)", "date": "2026-01-13T21:32:19+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - At the conclusion of debate on H.R. 2262, the Chair put the question on motion to recommit and by voice vote, announced the noes had prevailed. Mr. Norcross demanded the yeas and nays and the Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.", "date": "2026-01-13T19:32:33+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classi